  },
  "description": "Automated `claude -p` runs (pods/scripts), keyed on run.mode=automated. Segmented by run.role, run.task, run.user. Populates once automation sets OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES (see CLAUDE-CODE-OTEL.md).",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [
    {
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "/d/claude-code-usage",
      "icon": "dashboard"
    },
    {
      "title": "Automated",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "/d/claude-code-automated",
      "icon": "dashboard"
    },
    {
      "title": "Workflows",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "/d/claude-code-workflows",
      "icon": "dashboard"
    }
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Populating this dashboard",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "This view shows **automated** runs (`claude -p` in pods / scripts). It fills in once your automation sets `OTEL_RESOURCE_ATTRIBUTES` with at least:\n\n```\nrun.mode=automated,run.role=<coordinator|planner|developer|reviewer|\u2026>,run.user=<owner>,run.task=<ticket-id>,run.env=<local|ci|prod>\n```\n\nSet it in the pod spec / launcher. See `components/observability/grafana-dashboards/CLAUDE-CODE-OTEL.md`."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Headline (automated)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cost",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum(max_over_time({__name__=\"claude_code.cost.usage_USD_total\", \"run.mode\"=\"automated\", \"run.user\"=~\"$auser\", \"run.role\"=~\"$role\", \"run.task\"=~\"$task\", model=~\"$model\", effort=~\"$effort\", \"team.id\"=~\"$team\", \"run.env\"=~\"$env\", \"session.id\"=~\"$session\"}[$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "USD"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 25
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 100
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background_solid",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      }
    },
